    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * William Tunstall-Pedoe</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamtp/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/Tunstall-Pedoe.jpg/200px-Tunstall-Pedoe.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/f/f1/Tunstall-Pedoe.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Tunstall-Pedoe.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>William Tunstall-Pedoe <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>William Tunstall-Pedoe</b>,<br />\na British computer scientist, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a> entrepreneur, startup mentor, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angel_investor\">angel investor</a> and founder of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evi_(software)\">Evi</a>, formerly True Knowledge, which specializes in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge_base\">knowledge base</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semantic_search_engine\">semantic search</a> engine software. \nIn October 2012, Evi was acquired by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon_(company)\">Amazon</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, its technology and team became a key part of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon_Alexa\">Amazon Alexa</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Computer_Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Computer Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#AI_Software\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">AI Software</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Computer_Chess\">Computer Chess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William_Tunstall-Pedoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Computer Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>William Tunstall-Pedoe graduated from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Cambridge\">University of Cambridge</a> in 1991 - he wrote a CST Part II Dissertation describing <a href=\"/ACPP\" title=\"ACPP\">ACPP</a>, his advanced chess playing program, \nwhich was research vehicle in <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#GeneticAlgorithm\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">genetic algorithms</a> and <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">automated tuning</a> of <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> weights and <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> parameters, \nas elaborated in his <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#14_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal</a> paper <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \nIn 1992/93 he developed a complete commercial chess-playing program from scratch including a high quality chess engine, animated graphics, sound effects and a full state-of-the-art user interface. \nThe product was marketed as <a href=\"/Cyber_Chess\" title=\"Cyber Chess\">Cyber Chess</a> and published by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Fourth_Dimension_%28company%29\">The Fourth Dimension</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"AI_Software\">AI Software</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William_Tunstall-Pedoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: AI Software\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>From 1988 Tunstall-Pedoe developed and marketed various AI related software, most notably <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anagram\">Anagram</a> Genius</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> \nand since 1996 ,<i>Crossword Maestro</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> , a software which solves <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptic_crossword\">cryptic crossword</a> clues and explains in plain English how the clues work. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William_Tunstall-Pedoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>An Advanced Chess-Playing Program</i>. CST Part II Dissertation, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Cambridge\">University of Cambridge</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/\">Computer Laboratory</a>, England (unpublished, referred in <i>Genetic Algorithms ...</i>)</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Genetic Algorithms Optimizing Evaluation Functions</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#14_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 14, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a>, Donald L. Holmes (<b>1995</b>). <i>Anagram Genius: An Incredible Collection of Weird, Wonderful and Wacky Anagrams</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_English_Library\">New English Library Ltd.</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Anagram-Genius-Incredible-Collection-Wonderful/dp/0340657529/ref=sr_1_1?qid=1585162878&amp;refinements=p_27%3ADonald+L.+Holmes&amp;s=books&amp;sr=1-1\">Amazon.co.uk</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/ojs/index.php/aimagazine/article/view/2298\">True Knowledge: Open-Domain Question Answering Using Structured Knowledge and Inference</a></i>. <a href=\"/AAAI#AIMAG\" title=\"AAAI\">AI Magazine</a>, Vol. 31, No. 3</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William_Tunstall-Pedoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.williamtp.com/\">Personal site of William Tunstall-Pedoe</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.williamtp.com/blog/\">blog – William Tunstall-Pedoe</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamtp/\">William Tunstall-Pedoe | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/williamtp\">William Tunstall-Pedoe (@williamtp) / Twitter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mn2s.com/booking-agency/talent-roster/william-tunstall-pedoe/\">William Tunstall-Pedoe | Booking Agent | Speakers Roster | MN2S</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a> - The Origins of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon_Alexa\">Amazon Alexa</a>, 2019, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/HGaSgePBH4c?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William_Tunstall-Pedoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamtp/\">William Tunstall-Pedoe | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.evi.com/\">Evi - an Amazon Company</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2016-amazon-echo/\">The Real Story of How Amazon Built the Echo</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evi_(software)\">Evi (software) from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">William Tunstall-Pedoe</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Genetic Algorithms Optimizing Evaluation Functions</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#14_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 14, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20111114223548/http://www.williamtp.com/cv.html\">William Tunstall-Pedoe Resumé (Resume, Curriculum Vitae, CV)</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine, November 2011</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.anagramgenius.com/\">Anagram Genius - fun anagrams and anagram software</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.crosswordgenius.com/\">Home — Crossword Genius</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228102146\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.075 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.077 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 154/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 362/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6999-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228102146 and revision id 18516\n -->\n"
